// Unity Class: ScriptableObject
// Documentation: https://docs.unity3d.com/ScriptReference/ScriptableObject.html

// Description: A class you can derive from if you want to create objects that live independently of GameObjects.

// Properties:
// - hideFlags: Should the object be hidden, saved with the Scene or modifiable by the user?
// - name: The name of the object.

// Methods:
// - GetInstanceID: Gets the instance ID of the object.
// - ToString: Returns the name of the object.
// - CreateInstance: Creates an instance of a scriptable object.

